public class BeaTrace60
extends java.lang.Object
implements Trace

BeaTrace60.java This class uses Weblogic's NonCatalogLogger class to print debug output. Note that debug output is only visible in standard out, if you turn it on in Weblogic Server's admin console. This class was taken from Nokia's SA implemenation.
